data.text:
This site is actually a client on the Gnutella Network. With this site you can search for and download and share different types of files. The site itself is simple and at the top you will find the download link, features, support, about and open source. You can even get the site in different languages if needed.

The latest features section has info on creating and sharing lists face book, overhauled bit torrent, advanced search and virus protection along with costs from basic to extended pro. Get support and your questions answered. Under that you will find the wiki, forum, tech blog, music blog and careers.

You will find sections and explanations on the Gnutella Network, starting as a developer and running a UDP Host Cache. To the right side of the page there lists for downloads, contribute and developer resources. You can also read about the Lime wire Project complete with the License, awards, acknowledgements and careers at Lime Wire.

Learn things like how to build a source code, bugs and feature requests, translate and even volunteering. You can look at through the Music blog and Music Store. Get the newest Lime wire 5 in basic or pro and download easily right from the site.
